library(factoextra)
data("multishapes")

# kmeans
set.seed(1)
cl <- kmeans(df, 5)
df2 <- df
df2$cluster <- cl$cluster
df2 %>% 
  ggplot() +
  geom_point(aes(x = x, y = y, color = as.factor(cluster))) +
  theme_bw() +
  theme(text = element_text(family = "Hei")) +
  labs(color = "Cluster") +
